original_title: The Fish Bum Diaries: Volume 2 Metalhead
overview: Chronicles the epic journey of five fish bums and their friends as they travel to remote Northwestern wilderness in search of legendary steelhead; the hottest freshwater fish you can catch on a fly rod and also a fish whose survival hangs in the balance. 60 min.
title: The Fish Bum Diaries: Volume 2 Metalhead
